cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use zarr-matlab in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "zarr-matlab: Zarr v3 for MATLAB"
abstract: >-
  A pure-MATLAB implementation of the Zarr v3 chunked, compressed
  N-dimensional array storage specification, with byte-level
  interoperability against zarr-python verified in continuous
  integration. Supports sharding with partial reads, zstd/blosc/gzip/
  crc32c codecs, variable-length strings, datetime64, zip and HTTP
  stores, and consolidated metadata.
authors:
